<div class="ugc-mod reading-notes">
  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1044912/annotation">共<span property="v:count">6</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="24521302">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/38928437/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg" alt="臭包子" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24521302/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24521302/" class="">第448页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/38928437/" class=" " title="臭包子">臭包子</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24521302">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">即如一丘一壑,一小区处,甚至一矮檐下，一小窗前，亦随处有人生真乐可得，何必是名胜地，大建筑。陈抟之居华山，林逋隐西湖，同得人生乐处。古人云：“风景不殊，而举目有江山之异。”有和风，有轻阳，此即风景，到处可乐。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-02-11 21:24</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                即如一丘一壑,一小区处,甚至一矮檐下，一小窗前，亦随处有人生真乐可得，何必是名胜地，大建筑。陈抟之居华山，林逋隐西湖，同得人生乐处。古人云：“风景不殊，而举目有江山之异。”有和风，有轻阳，此即风景，到处可乐。
